This is plugin for JIRA

It's provide a mutable list of employee (Department, Name, Position, Internal and External phone number, e-mail, Birthday and photo).

Highlights the birthday.

Search engine for all fields.

The name is not related with Jira users for more flexibility.

Editing is allowed for the user who is part of the 'HR360' group.

https://marketplace.atlassian.com/plugins/ua.softlist.employee.employees-list/server/overview